-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-UgY6rJA1NT1_K0Mp948lcA">Nga My sơn nguyệt - 峨嵋山月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%A1t-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%91c-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-VmdDx8oi1-YcvXe8X2T_Ww">Phát Đồng Cốc huyện - 發同谷縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc/poem-SHato7hti_kk6NTDzvifYA">Tái hạ khúc - 塞下曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/author-AGCqPCIFskZR14TGi3NQzg">Chu Phác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%93ng-V%E1%BB%8Bnh/Th%E1%BB%ABa-L%C6%B0u-hi%E1%BB%83u-ph%C3%A1t/poem-neOUZMWGA0ao1kMt1mpc9g">Thừa Lưu hiểu phát - 承留曉發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%93ng-V%E1%BB%8Bnh/author-E6a5e7SOI8-d6_k05ZXmwg">Nguyễn Phúc Hồng Vịnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
